;;       |_____| |_______________| |_| |_________________________________________|
;;        <from>    <to>      <conditions>         <other options>

;; !  | means mandatory
;; #  | means optional
;; C  | left_command
;; T  | left_control
;; O  | left_option
;; S  | left_shift
;; F  | fn
;; Q  | right_command
;; W  | right_control
;; E  | right_option
;; R  | right_shift
;;
;; !! | mandatory command + control + optional + shift (hyper)
;; ## | optional any
;;
